291&ndash;309.</li>

<li>Moss, Sarah, 2011, &ldquo;Scoring Rules and Epistemic
Compromise,&rdquo; <em>Mind</em>, 120(480): 1053&ndash;1069.
doi:10.1093/mind/fzs007</li>

<li>Nguyen, C. T., 2020, &ldquo;Echo chambers and epistemic
bubbles,&rdquo; <em>Episteme</em>, 17(2): 141&ndash;161.</li>

